<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Usage<sp/>would<sp/>be<sp/>something<sp/>like:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>import<sp/>libembroidery<sp/>as<sp/>emb</highlight></codeline>
