<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>python3<sp/>setup.py<sp/>install<sp/>--user</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">from<sp/>the<sp/>top<sp/>level.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
